#

Pumpkin Seed and Avocado Toast

5 min
$3.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

QuickHealthySnackBreakfast

Description

A quick and nutritious toast topped with creamy avocado and crunchy pumpkin seeds, perfect for breakfast or a snack!

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • ripe avocado: 1
  • pumpkin seeds: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes (optional): to taste
